    <decisions>
        <description>This flow supports passing in an Account Id as the owner for the Case. But if none was passed in, we&apos;ll assume this Case is being created by a Community User. In that case, we need to retrieve the current user&apos;s related ContactId and AccountId.</description>
        <name>Decide_Need_to_Retrieve_Contact</name>
